<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA626_06_IH_0004</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema626_06_ih_0004.js"></script>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema626_06.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema626_06_ih_0004">
			<section class="title type2">
				<h2 data-head="4_orange" lang="y">구에 대해 옳게 설명한 것에 ○표, 잘못 설명한 것에 ×표 하세요.</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="question_box justify_center align_center">
					<div class="drag_checkout">
						<div class="draggable_wrap">
							<span class="single_draggable draggable circle"></span>
							<span class="single_draggable draggable triangle"></span>
						</div>

						<ul
							class="drag_group g1"
							data-group-limit="3"
							data-answer-single="[[true, false], [false, true], [false, true]]"
						>
							<li class="item1">
								<p class="text_bullet" lang="y">구의 중심은 셀 수 없이 많습니다.</p>
								<div class="l_right">
									(
									<span class="droppable" data-value="false false"> </span>
									)
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="item2">
								<p class="text_bullet" lang="y">구의 반지름은 셀 수 없이 많고, 길이가 모두 같습니다.</p>
								<div class="l_right">
									(
									<span class="droppable" data-value="false false"> </span>
									)
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="item3">
								<p class="text_bullet" lang="y">구의 지름은 구의 중심을 지납니다.</p>
								<div class="l_right">
									(
									<span class="droppable" data-value="false false"> </span>
									)
								</div>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- 해설 -->
				<div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
								<p lang="y">구의 중심은 구에서 가장 안쪽에 있는 점이므로 1개입니다.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<!-- <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button> -->
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
